Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Feet MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Effusion' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And Localizer is enabled

When I click on the Localizer
And select two parts on the Localizer canvas
And close the canvas
Then 'Mild' radio button is disabled
And 'Significant' radio button is disabled
And 'Haemarthros' radio button is disabled
And 'Capsule rupture' radio button is disabled
And 'Loose Fragment' checkbox is disabled
